Description: Edit Markdown locally or over SSH/SFTP
 VertexWrite is a GTK3/WebKit desktop app for opening, previewing, and editing
 Markdown documents wherever they live: local folders or remote servers over
 SSH/SFTP. It provides preview mode, live split view editing, syntax
 highlighting, command palette navigation, folder search, checkbox/task
 toggling, and optional export through pandoc.
